<p>
“I love it when a plans comes together” by John ‘Hannibal’ Smith (A-Team) is famous phrase that in a way sums up why I like programming so much. I’m very fortunate because I get to experience this feeling rather often after struggling and racking my brain to build lots of small intricate parts that at the end come together. And like every episode, the bigger and more intense the challenge is - the more interesting and exciting it is to work on. 
</p>
<p>
