</p>
<p>
I’m very curious, eager to learn and quick to pick up new skills. I believe I can quickly become a valuable part of a team and work really well with others as well as on my own. As a programmer I would love to be in an environment that nurtures learning and keeps challenging the mind.
And as a person I just want to do something meaningful, stimulating and fun all the time.
</p>
